<div class="post-15308 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-fi-news category-news">
<a href="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/news/your-renewal-date-is-changing/"  title="Your renewal date is changing"><img src="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Flag-Institute-logo_verysmall-100x100.png" alt=""  width="100"  height="100"  class="woo-image thumbnail alignleft" /></a><h2 class="title"><a href="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/news/your-renewal-date-is-changing/" rel="bookmark" title="Your renewal date is changing">Your renewal date is changing</a></h2><div class="post-meta"><span class="small">By</span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/author/admin_james/" title="Posts by Webmaster" rel="author">Webmaster</a></span></span> <span class="small">on</span> <abbr class="date time published" title="2024-04-01T15:27:31+0100">1 April 2024</abbr>  <span class="small">in</span> <span class="categories"><a href="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/category/fi-news/">FI News</a>, <a href="https://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/category/news/">News</a></span>   </div>
	<div class="entry">
	    <p>Please note an upcoming change in your membership renewal date. From 1 July 2024 the following dates will apply: 1 October 2024, and each 1 October thereafter: – all members joining or due to renew 1 July–31 December 2024 1 April 2025, and each 1 April thereafter: – all members joining or due to renew [&hellip;]</p>
	</div><!-- /.entry -->
